data.description: Modern country luxury home with multi generation options. This home is a must see as many great features can not be described. Custom built ICF construction on 3 acres with incredible views in Brookside. Main level features open great room and primary suite on one side with deck access. Walkout lower level with full kitchen, living room, bedroom and bath. Attached one car garage with laundry. Private exterior entry and stairs behind book shelves to upper level. 329 SF casita with bedroom, bath, and kitchenette. 2 car garage with storage cabinets and work bench. Enjoy the quiet and dark sky from the large deck and patio. The Santa Clara River is close by for fishing or a relaxing stroll. Hundreds of miles of roads to explore on ATV's, mountain bikes right out your door. Year round access
